## Terms [/terms.json]

The `terms` type has the
[mapping](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/mapping.html) above:

```
'terms': {
  'properties': {
    'date': {
      'type': 'date'
    },
    'term': {
      'type': 'string'
    },
    'results': {
      'type': 'short'
    },
    'count': {
      'type': 'integer'
    }
  }
}
```

### Terms Simple Search [GET /terms.json?q={field}:{value}]

[URI Search](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-uri-request.html)

+ Parameters
    + field: `term` (string, required) - Valid term object property
    + value: `t-shirt` (string, required) - Value to be searched

+ Response 200 (application/json)

